# 🌧️ Rainfall Prediction Project  

## 📌 Overview  
This project predicts **rainfall** (Yes/No) using **machine learning algorithms**.  
It takes weather features (temperature, pressure, humidity, etc.) as input and predicts whether it will rain or not.  

The workflow:  
1. Load dataset  
2. Explore and clean data  
3. Train multiple ML models  
4. Evaluate accuracy  
5. Predict rainfall from **user input**  
6. Save and reload the trained model  

