🤖 Algorithms Used

Logistic Regression → Classifies rainfall based on probabilities.

Decision Tree → Splits features into rules for prediction.

Random Forest → Multiple trees combined for higher accuracy.

K-Nearest Neighbors (KNN) → Finds similar weather conditions to predict rainfall.

The best model is chosen by comparing accuracy scores.

